column5: Went out today with a friend east of ferry after some eyes. We had a pretty good day, caught 3 fish all about 6lb-7lb range. Started fishing around 7:30am and finished around 1:30. All the fish we caught in 85ft-95ft. of water down 30ft-40ft. I will be out again next week and hopefully post some positive results. Good Luck and hope to see you guys on the water. Look for a TRACKER boat.
nice looks like I will be getting down there soon
